@@ -1,7 +1,11 @@
-# Always Use the Best Models
+# The Synch Rule: Micro vs Macro Tasks
 
-**Connect your keys for Anthropic (Claude), Google (Gemini), OpenAI (GPT), and other leading LLMs.**
+**Manage micro-tasks in chat. Update state only at milestones.**
 
-Cline puts you at the forefront of AI. Bring your own API keys for leading models like Anthropic (Claude), Google (Gemini), and OpenAI (GPT). Always leverage the most powerful State-of-the-Art (SOTA) capabilities, ensuring you control both cost and cutting-edge performance.
+- **Micro-Tasks**: Checkboxes and small TODOs stay in the chat (your RAM)
+- **Macro-State**: Only update `01_state.md` when reaching milestones (your Hard Drive)
+- **Why?** This prevents clutter and maintains a clean long-term memory
 
-![Cline Models Demo](https://storage.googleapis.com/cline_public_images/docs/assets/clines-models-hifi-3_compress.webp)
+`01_state.md` is for future sessions. The chat is for the current session.
+
+![Resonance Synch Rule](https://storage.googleapis.com/cline_public_images/docs/assets/clines-models-hifi-3_compress.webp)
